Transfer.particulars: Note:Please keep the deposit slip as proof of payment
Transfer.occurs:
1.The first seven digits of the Transfer account number are fixed at 9001136 or 9001138 or 90042116 or 90042117 or 94507. Any request to transfer funds to an account that does not follow this rule is fraud!
2.Please ensure the account information is correct, otherwise the repayment will not be successful and you may not be able to recover funds from an incorrect transfer.
